trans-unit.source: Provides the XAML type system identifier for a member if the member is also a XAML directive.
trans-unit.target: Gir XAML system typeidentifikatoren for et medlem hvis medlemmet også er en XAML-direktivet.

trans-unit.source: XAML readers and XAML writers use the XamlDirective identifier during processing of member nodes.
trans-unit.target: XAML lesere og XAML skrivere Bruk XamlDirective-ID under behandling av medlem noder.

trans-unit.source: The identifier is used when the XAML reader is positioned on a <xref href="System.Xaml.XamlNodeType"></xref> and <xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember.IsDirective*> is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Identifikatoren brukes når XAML-leseren er plassert på en <xref href="System.Xaml.XamlNodeType"> </xref> og <xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember.IsDirective*>er <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref>.</xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember.IsDirective*>

trans-unit.source: XamlDirective provides expected values for the XAML type system when the member is a XAML directive.
trans-unit.target: XamlDirective gir forventede verdier for XAML typen systemet når medlemmet er en XAML-direktivet.

trans-unit.source: By definition, a XAML directive has characteristics that always return the same results for a subset of the <xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember> properties, and the same XAML type system information is reported for all possible XAML directives.
trans-unit.target: XAML-direktivet er egenskaper som returnerer alltid samme resultatene for et delsett av ved definisjon av <xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember>Egenskaper og samme XAML system typeinformasjonen rapporteres for alle mulige XAML-direktivene.</xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember>

trans-unit.source: The reporting of XAML type system characteristics that are specific to directives is accomplished by internal behavior or through overrides of <xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember> `Lookup*` virtual members in the XamlDirective class.
trans-unit.target: Rapportering av XAML system egenskaper som er spesifikke for direktivene oppnås ved interne virkemåten eller gjennom overstyring av <xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember> `Lookup*` virtuelle medlemmer i klassen. XamlDirective</xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember>
